nodes.text: Sector Delta was a district of the mysterious space station known as Zirtran's Anchor. It was the location of a number of various different businesses and services and also served as residence of a number of famous and infamous individuals.
The most well lnown locations in Sector Delta were the Death Mark, Reenogga Personal Services, Cubed, the Rusted Cutlass II, and the Laughing Sullustan.
